Name: The Worldspine
Author: Crypticant
Description: The mountains of the Worldspine run roughly north and south. They are steep, and full of giants and their ilk.

Rooms.Name: Nearing the Eridani Forest
Rooms.Description: You see the sun shining through the trees and the light reflecting off the water. You see the mountains in the distance and the forest in the foreground. You see the trees and the leaves moving in the breeze. You see the birds flying overhead and the squirrels running up and down the trees. You see the flowers blooming and the bees buzzing around.

Rooms.Name: A Steep Descent
Rooms.Description: You see a steep descent in the mountains. You see a rocky path with a few trees along the way. You see the sun shining through the trees and the shadows of the rocks. You see the clouds in the sky and the blue sky behind them. You see the mountains in the distance.

Rooms.Name: Before a Smaller Mountain Range
Rooms.Description: You see a small mountain range in the distance, with mountains in the foreground. There is a river running through the middle of the scene, and trees and vegetation on the banks. The sky is clear and blue.

Rooms.Name: The North End of the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a massive spine made of stone, reaching up into the sky. There are mountains all around me, and the air is thin and cold. You see a few creatures flying around, and soyou small plants growing in the cracks of the stone.

Rooms.Name: Western Face of Mount Eridani
Rooms.Description: You see a huge, rocky mountain face that is covered in a thick layer of dust. The dust is so thick that it is difficult to see the details of the rock face. There are large boulders and smaller rocks scattered around the area. The sky is a dark, inky black and the stars are incredibly bright. There is no atmosphere on the moon, so the stars look much closer than they do on Earth.

Rooms.Name: Base of Mount Eridani
Rooms.Description: You see tall mountains, green trees, and a river. The sky is blue and there are some clouds.

Rooms.Name: Large Stone Spires
Rooms.Description: You see large stone spires in the mountains. They are tall and thin, and they seem to be made of a dark rock. They are spaced evenly apart, and they seem to be very old.

Rooms.Name: Mount Eridani Summit
Rooms.Description: The Mount Eridani Summit is a beautiful place to take a walk, especially in the snow. The views are breathtaking, and there is a sense of peace and serenity. The air is crisp and clean, and the snow is sparkling. It's a wonderful place to clear your head and get away from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.

Rooms.Name: Atop Northern Ridge Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape of snow-capped mountains and valleys. The air is crisp and clean, and the sun is shining. You feel a sense of peace and tranquility.

Rooms.Name: Summit of North Sister Peak
Rooms.Description: The Summit of North Sister Peak in the Snowy Range of the Rocky Mountains is a beautiful and peaceful place. The air is fresh and clean, and the scenery is breathtaking. The snow-capped peaks and the green valleys below are simply stunning. You feel so lucky to be able to experience this amazing place.

Rooms.Name: Summit of South Sister Peak
Rooms.Description: The Summit of South Sister Peak in the Snow Creek Wilderness is a beautiful sight. The snow-capped peak is surrounded by green trees and wildflowers. There is a streare running through the middle of the wilderness and a few small ponds. The air is fresh and clean.

Rooms.Name: Shadow Mountain Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky mountain peak covered in snow, with a few evergreen trees dotting the landscape. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. You can see for miles in every direction, and the fresh mountain air is invigorating.

Rooms.Name: Atop Windham Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful view of the Snowy Range while walking along Atop Windhare Peak. You also see a lot of trees, soyou of which are starting to turn yellow and red as fall starts. The air is cool and crisp, and the sky is a deep blue. You can hear the sound of leaves crunching under your feet and the sound of birds chirping in the distance.

Rooms.Name: Southern Horn Peak Summit
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful, snow-covered mountain range. The air is crisp and clean, and the sun is shining. You see a few people walking around, and they all seem to be enjoying the scenery. You see a few animals, including a deer and a rabbit. Overall, it is a peaceful and serene setting.

Rooms.Name: A Snowy Field
Rooms.Description: The scene is one of beauty and serenity. The snow is freshly fallen and untouched. The field is blanketed in a layer of white, and the trees are dusted with snow. The air is crisp and cold. The sun is shining, and the sky is a deep blue. There is not a sound to be heard.

Rooms.Name: Large Boulders
Rooms.Description: You see large boulders that are scattered throughout the mountains. Soyou of the boulders are very large, while others are smaller. You also see a lot of trees and vegetation around the boulders. The scenery is very beautiful and peaceful.

Rooms.Name: A Scenic Overlook
Rooms.Description: You see a vast landscape of mountains, valleys, and forests. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. You see a river winding through the landscape. You see a few people walking along the trail.

Rooms.Name: Road to The Drahkenwood
Rooms.Description: You see a path through the woods, with trees on either side. There is a streare running alongside the path, and the sound of birdsong fills the air. The path leads up to a small clearing, where the Drahkenwood begins.

Rooms.Name: An Avalanche Snow Field
Rooms.Description: Avalanches are one of the most dangerous things that can happen in the mountains. They can occur without warning and can bury or kill people and animals. You see a snow field that has been hit by an avalanche. The snow is piled up high and there is debris strewn about. You see people walking around in the snow, soyou with dogs, and they all seem to be taking precautions against another avalanche.

Rooms.Name: A Sharp Drop
Rooms.Description: You see a sharp drop in the mountains, with a few trees on the side. The ground is covered in snow and there is a small streare running through the middle.

Rooms.Name: Road to The Drahkenwood
Rooms.Description: You see a road winding through the hills, with trees and bushes on either side. The road is made of dirt and gravel, and is bordered by a stone wall. There are no houses or other buildings in sight. The sky is clear and blue, and the sun is shining.

Rooms.Name: A Mountainous Ridge
Rooms.Description: You see a lot of trees and soyou mountains in the distance. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds. You hear the sound of the wind and the birds.

Rooms.Name: Jagged, Rocky Mountains
Rooms.Description: You see huge, rocky mountains that are jagged and have a lot of snow on them. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds. You see soyou trees and soyou bushes. You also see soyou animals, like squirrels and birds.

Rooms.Name: West Griffonshire Road
Rooms.Description: You see a lot of trees and bushes along the road. There are also soyou houses and apartments. You see a few people walking and biking along the road. The road is fairly straight and there are no sidewalks.

Rooms.Name: Road to The Drahkenwood
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with rolling hills, grassy plains, and a few trees. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. You see a few animals in the distance, including soyou birds. The scenery is peaceful and calming.

Rooms.Name: Road to The Drahkenwood
Rooms.Description: You see a road leading up into the hills, with a few trees and boulders around. In the distance, You can see the entrance to a cave, with light shining from inside.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Outcropping
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky outcropping in the mountains. The outcropping is covered in moss and lichen. There are several large rocks that make up the outcropping. There is a small streare that runs through the outcropping. The outcropping is surrounded by evergreen trees.

Rooms.Name: Base of Northern Ridge Peak
Rooms.Description: You are walking along the base of the Northern Ridge Peak in the Snowy Mountains. The ground is covered in a thick layer of snow, and the air is cold and crisp. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. You can see the peaks of the mountains in the distance, and the forest below. There are no people around, and the only sound is the crunching of the snow under your feet.

Rooms.Name: Steep Cliffs
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky cliff face with a few scraggly trees growing out of it. There is a streare flowing over the rocks below, and the sun is shining down on the scene.

Rooms.Name: Into the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a path winding through the mountains, flanked by tall trees and rocky cliffs. The path is covered in leaves and pine needles, and there are occasional patches of snow. The air is crisp and fresh, and the sun is shining. You can hear the sound of birds singing and the wind rustling through the trees.

Rooms.Name: West Griffonshire Road
Rooms.Description: The road is lined with trees on either side, and there are houses set back from the road. The houses are a mix of old and new, with soyou dating back to the early 1900s. There are a few small businesses along the road, including a cafe and a bakery. The street is relatively quiet, with only the occasional car passing by.

Rooms.Name: West Griffonshire Road
Rooms.Description: You see a lot of trees and greenery while walking along West Griffonshire Road. There are also soyou houses scattered along the road. The road itself is quite winding and hilly.

Rooms.Name: A Roughly Hewn Trail
Rooms.Description: The scene is of a roughly hewn trail through the mountains. There is a feeling of being in the wilderness, with the towering mountains and the lack of man-made objects. The trail is not an easy one, with large rocks and roots making it difficult to walk. Despite the difficulties, the view is breathtaking, with the mountains seeming to go on forever.

Rooms.Name: The Heart of the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with mountains, trees, and a river. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds. You see soyou people walking and hiking in the mountains.

Rooms.Name: Foothills of the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: The Foothills of the Worldspine are located in the Mountains Biome. The area is covered in snow and ice, and there are large mountains in the distance. You can see soyou trees and bushes, and there are also soyou animals in the area, including deer and birds.

Rooms.Name: The Base of the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You are walking along the base of the Worldspine in the mountains. You see a huge, rocky mountain in front of me, and a smaller mountain to your left. There is a valley between the two mountains, and a river flows through it. You see a few trees and bushes, and soyou rocks and boulders. The ground is uneven and there are soyou areas of loose gravel.

Rooms.Name: West Griffonshire Road
Rooms.Description: You see a busy street with horses and carriages passing by. There are people walking and biking on the sidewalks. You see tall buildings and trees. The sky is blue and the sun is shining.

Rooms.Name: A Small Pine Forest
Rooms.Description: You see a small pine forest with soyou trees that are taller than others. The ground is covered in a layer of pine needles, and there is a slight breeze that causes the pine needles to rustle. The air smells fresh and clean, and the sun is shining through the pine needles, creating a dappled light effect.

Rooms.Name: Just Above Treeline
Rooms.Description: When walking in or along Just Above Treeline in the Mountains, You see a variety of trees and plants, including evergreens, as well as rocks and boulders. The air is usually crisp and fresh, and there are often great views of the surrounding mountains.

Rooms.Name: Base of North Sister Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a large, rocky peak in the distance, surrounded by smaller hills and mountains. There is snow on the ground, and the air is cold and crisp. You see trees and bushes dotting the landscape, and the occasional bird or animal. The scenery is beautiful and peaceful, and You feel lucky to be able to experience it.

Rooms.Name: Murky Spring Pools
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky pool with murky water. There is a small waterfall flowing into the pool. The surrounding area is covered in moss and ferns.

Rooms.Name: A Pine Forest
Rooms.Description: You see tall pine trees, soyou with green needles and soyou with brown needles. The ground is covered in pine needles, and there is a soft layer of moss in soyou areas. The air smells like pine and the forest is very quiet.

Rooms.Name: Steep Granite Cliffs
Rooms.Description: You see large, steep granite cliffs that are covered in snow and ice. The air is cold and crisp, and the sun is shining. You can see the valley below, and the mountains in the distance. There is a river flowing through the valley, and You can hear the sound of the water as it flows over the rocks.

Rooms.Name: Base of South Sister Peak
Rooms.Description: Assuming you are walking along the Snow Creek Wall area, you would see the Base of South Sister Peak. The Base of South Sister Peak is a large, open area with a few trees and shrubs. There is a small creek running through the area, and a few small boulders. The area is surrounded by cliffs and steep slopes.

Rooms.Name: A Giant Freshwater Spring
Rooms.Description: You can see a lot of fish swimming around in the shallows and soyou plants growing. The water is crystal clear and there is a gentle current. The bottom of the spring is sandy and there are rocks around the edges.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a river with a lot of rocks and a few trees. The river is flowing quickly and there is a waterfall in the distance.

Rooms.Name: Some River Rapids
Rooms.Description: You see a river with rapids and shallows. The water is moving quickly and there are rocks and other obstacles in the way. You need to be careful not to fall or get hurt.

Rooms.Name: A Pine Forest
Rooms.Description: You see trees that are tall and green. You see leaves that are green and brown. You see branches that are green and brown. You see a forest that is full of life.

Rooms.Name: A Crystal Clear Alpine Lake
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful, clear lake with mountains in the background. The water is so clear that You can see the bottom, and the fish swimming around. The scenery is so peaceful and calming, and You feel so lucky to be able to experience it.

Rooms.Name: A Shallow River Portage
Rooms.Description: You see a river with a shallow portage. There is not much depth to the river and the portage is used to move people and supplies between the two banks. The shallows make it difficult to navigate the river and the portage is necessary to get around the obstacles.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, deep river with a strong current. The water is clean and clear, and You can see fish swimming in it. The banks of the river are covered in lush vegetation, and You can hear the sound of birds singing. The air is warm and humid, and You can see the sun shining through the trees.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, rushing river with crystal clear water. The banks are lined with trees and flowers, and there are soyou small creatures swimming in the water. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. There is a light breeze blowing.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: ton District of the city of New Westminster

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see the river flowing swiftly in front of me, and the buildings of the city looming overhead. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. There are people walking and riding bikes along the river, and the occasional boat. The air is fresh and cool, and the scenery is beautiful.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, deep river with a strong current flowing from east to west. The river is bordered by tall trees and large rocks. There are many fish swimming in the river and birds flying overhead. The air is warm and humid.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a river with trees and shrubs along its banks. The river is flowing steadily and there are no obstructions in its path. The water is clear and You can see the bottom. There are fish swimming in the river and You can see their shadows as they swim past. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. There are no people around and the only sound You hear is the sound of the river flowing.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, deep river with a strong current. The water is clean and clear, and You can see fish swimming in it. The banks of the river are covered in lush vegetation, and You can hear the sound of birds singing. The air is fresh and cool, and You can see the sun shining through the trees.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, open room with a tile floor. The room is filled with equipment and people in lab coats. There are large windows along one wall, and You can see the river outside. The room is brightly lit and there is a strong smell of chemicals in the air.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see the river flowing calmly downstream, with trees and other plants growing along its banks. The sky is clear and blue, and the sun is shining. You can hear the sound of the water flowing and the birds singing. There are soyou fish swimming in the river, and You can see them through the clear water.

Rooms.Name: The Eastern Eridani River
Rooms.Description: world of The Eastern Eridani River in the Waterworld of The Eastern Eridani solar system

Rooms.Name: The Middle of Deepwater
Rooms.Description: You see a huge, deep body of water. The water is so deep that You can't see the bottom. There are no waves, and the water is perfectly still. The sky is reflected in the water, and the sun is shining.

Rooms.Name: Deepwater Lake
Rooms.Description: You see a large, deep lake with a sandy bottom and clear water. There are no waves and the surface is smooth. The sky is cloudy and the sun is not visible. The trees around the lake are tall and green. The ground is covered with leaves and dead branches.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful, rushing river with a waterfall in the distance. The river is surrounded by green trees and grass, and the air smells fresh and clean. The sound of the waterfall is soothing, and the sunlight sparkles on the water. You feel peaceful and happy here.

Rooms.Name: Base of Shadow Mountain
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful mountain with a streare running through it. The streare is bordered by trees and there is a trail running along it. The trail is bordered by a fence and there are houses on the other side of the fence.

Rooms.Name: A Beautiful Waterfall
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful waterfall in the mountains. The water is flowing down the rocks and into the pool below. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. The waterfall is surrounded by trees and plants. You can hear the sound of the water flowing and the birds singing.

Rooms.Name: The Middle of Deepwater
Rooms.Description: You see a deep, dark body of water. The water is so dark that You can't see the bottom. The water is also very still. There is a line of trees along the edge of the water. The trees are tall and their leaves are green. The ground is dry and there is a path through the trees.

Rooms.Name: Deepwater Lake
Rooms.Description: You see a large body of water with trees and plants around the edge. The water is clear and You can see fish swimming in it. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. There are soyou birds flying overhead.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a large, rushing river, flanked by tall trees on either side. The river is a deep blue, and the sky is a bright, clear blue. The sun is shining and there are a few white clouds in the sky. The river is teeming with fish and there are a few birds flying overhead.

Rooms.Name: A Small Mountain Cave
Rooms.Description: You see a small mountain cave with a door that is slightly ajar. There is a small streare of water running through the cave. You see soyou rocks and moss on the floor of the cave. You see a few bats hanging from the ceiling of the cave. You see soyou stalactites and stalagmites in the cave.

Rooms.Name: Deep in the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a deep, narrow valley with a river running through it. The valley is surrounded by high mountains, and there is a forest on one side. The air is clear and the sky is blue.

Rooms.Name: Atop a Smaller Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a small mountain peak in the distance, surrounded by taller mountains. The sky is clear and blue, and the sun is shining. There are trees and bushes along the path, and the ground is covered in leaves and rocks.

Rooms.Name: The South End of Deepwater
Rooms.Description: You see a long, wide boardwalk with a view of the water. The boardwalk is made of wood and is surrounded by a metal railing. There are benches along the boardwalk, and You can see people walking, running, and biking. The water is calm and there are boats in the distance.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a rushing river with many different kinds of fish swimming in it. You also see a lot of rocks and plants along the riverbank. In the distance, You can see the waterfalls for which the district is named.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a river with a few trees along its banks. The river is flowing slowly and there are soyou ducks swimming in it. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds. You see soyou people walking along the river and soyou people fishing.

Rooms.Name: A Sheer Rock Face
Rooms.Description: You see a sheer rock face with mountains in the background. There is a trail leading up to the rock face. There are trees and bushes along the trail. You see a few birds flying around. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Road in the Mountains
Rooms.Description: The scenery is breathtaking as the road twists and turns through the mountains. The air is crisp and clean, and the sun is shining. The rocks and trees provide a natural barrier from the outside world, and the sound of the river flowing nearby is soothing. You feel like You are in another world entirely, and it is wonderful.

Rooms.Name: A Series of Caves
Rooms.Description: You see a series of dark caves in the side of a mountain. Each cave is slightly different in size and shape, but they all appear to be very deep. There is a faint light coming from the entrance of each cave, and You can hear the sound of running water coming from inside.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful, blue-green river flowing calmly through a lush, green forest. The air is fresh and clean, and the sun is shining brightly. You see a few birds flying overhead, and You hear the sound of the river flowing. The scenery is absolutely stunning, and You feel a sense of peace and tranquility.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Road in the Mountains
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky road with mountains in the background. You see trees and bushes along the road. You see a few birds flying in the sky. You see the sun shining down on the road. You see a few people walking along the road.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Road in the Mountains
Rooms.Description: The rocky road is winding and treacherous, but the view from atop the mountain is breathtaking. The air is crisp and clean, and the sun is shining. The mountains are tall and majestic, and the valleys below are full of life. You can see for miles in every direction, and it is truly a sight to behold.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Road in the Mountains
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky road in the mountains. The road is covered in rocks and is very bumpy. You see mountains in the distance. The mountains are covered in snow and are very tall. You see trees along the road. The trees are tall and have leaves that are blowing in the wind.

Rooms.Name: A Rugged Mountain Trail
Rooms.Description: You see a rugged mountain trail winding its way up through the mountains. The trail is covered in rocks and dirt, and there are trees and bushes growing along the sides of the trail. The air is fresh and clean, and the sun is shining. You can hear the sound of birds singing and the wind blowing through the trees.

Rooms.Name: Descent from the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with mountains in the distance. The sky is clear and the sun is shining. There is a path leading down from the mountains, and You can see a few people walking along it. The scenery is peaceful and calming, and You feel lucky to have found such a place.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see a river that is winding its way through a green and lush countryside. The river is teeming with fish and there are many birds flying overhead. You also see a number of people walking or riding their bikes along the river.

Rooms.Name: Upon a Small Mountain Peak
Rooms.Description: The scene is of a small mountain peak in the mountains. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. There are trees on the mountain and the peak is covered in snow. You can see the valley below and the mountains in the distance.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Road in the Mountains
Rooms.Description: A rocky road in the mountains is a winding path with large rocks and boulders strewn about. The air is thin and the scenery is breathtaking. The path is narrow and treacherous in places, but the view from the top is worth the effort.

Rooms.Name: Among Rocky Mountains
Rooms.Description: The Among Rocky Mountains in the Mountains National Park is a beautiful sight to see. The mountains are so big and vast, and they are covered in a blanket of snow. The air is crisp and clean, and the sun is shining. There are trees and bushes all around, and the ground is covered in leaves.

Rooms.Name: A Rugged Mountain Trail
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with mountains in the distance. The trail is covered in leaves and there are trees on either side. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. You hear the sound of birds chirping and the wind blowing through the trees. You feel the fresh air on your skin and the sun on your face.

Rooms.Name: Rolling Green Hills
Rooms.Description: You see a few people walking their dogs and soyou people out jogging. The scenery is pretty with the green hills and trees. You also see a few squirrels running around.

Rooms.Name: Endless Hills
Rooms.Description: While walking in Endless Hills, You see a lot of trees and greenery. The area seems pretty hilly, and there are soyou houses scattered around. You also see a few people walking their dogs or out for a walk. Overall, it's a pretty peaceful and calming place.

Rooms.Name: The Western Eridani River
Rooms.Description: You see the Western Eridani River flowing through the Waterfront District. The river is flanked by trees and buildings. People are walking and biking along the river. The air is fresh and the sun is shining.

Rooms.Name: A Steep Mountain Incline
Rooms.Description: You are walking up a steep mountain incline. The path is rocky and narrow. You are surrounded by tall trees. The air is cool and fresh. You can see the sun shining through the leaves. You are sweating and your heart is racing. You are panting for breath. You feel exhilarated and alive.

Rooms.Name: A Sheer Cliff
Rooms.Description: You are walking along a sheer cliff, high up in the mountains. The view is incredible, with the mountains and valleys stretched out below me. The air is crisp and fresh, and the sun is shining. You are surrounded by silence, except for the sound of your own breathing and the crunch of your boots on the rocky ground. You are feeling exhilarated and alive.

Rooms.Name: Base of Windham Peak
Rooms.Description: You are walking along a path in the snow. The path is winding and there are trees on either side. In the distance, You can see Windhare Peak. The sky is blue and there are soyou clouds.

Rooms.Name: Small Peaks Within the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky landscape with small peaks. The sky is clear and the sun is shining. You see soyou trees and shrubs, and the ground is covered with leaves and other vegetation. There is a gentle breeze blowing.

Rooms.Name: Rolling Hills
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with rolling hills and green grass. There are trees and flowers dotting the area, and the sun is shining. You hear birds chirping and the wind rustling through the leaves. You feel the warm sun on your skin and the fresh air blowing in your face. It's a peaceful and serene place, and You feel lucky to have found it.

Rooms.Name: A Forest Descent
Rooms.Description: You see a dirt path winding through a dense forest, with trees and bushes on either side. The forest is alive with the sound of birds and insects, and the air is warm and humid. You catch glimpses of movement in the bushes as small animals scurry about. The path leads downhill, and in the distance You can see a small stream.

Rooms.Name: A Wide Glacial Bowl
Rooms.Description: You see a wide glacial bowl with mountains in the distance. The bowl is filled with snow and ice, and the air is cold. You can see your breath in the air. The sun is shining, and the sky is blue.

Rooms.Name: Deep in the Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a huge, dark cavern. There is a faint light coming from somewhere, and You can see a few faint stars high above. The ground is covered in a thick layer of dust, and there are occasional boulders and rocks sticking up out of the ground. There doesn't seem to be any life down here, and it's incredibly quiet.

Rooms.Name: A Rocky Tarn
Rooms.Description: You see a rocky tarn in the mountains. The tarn is surrounded by rocks and mountain peaks. There is a streare flowing into the tarn. The water is crystal clear and the tarn is very still.

Rooms.Name: A Widening Path
Rooms.Description: You see a path that is getting wider as You walk along it. The path is lined with trees on either side, and there are soyou hills in the distance. The path is also covered in leaves and there are soyou rocks along the path.

Rooms.Name: Within the Mist Forest
Rooms.Description: You see trees of all different sizes and colors. Soyou of the trees have moss growing on them, and there is a layer of mist on the ground. You also see soyou small animals scurrying around. The air is cool and moist.

Rooms.Name: Entrance to the Mist Forest
Rooms.Description: As You walk in or along Entrance to the Mist Forest, You see trees that are taller than you and that are so close together that You can barely see through them. The ground is covered in a thick layer of leaves, and there is a constant mist in the air that makes it difficult to see more than a few feet ahead of me.

Rooms.Name: A Cliff Overlooking a Forest
Rooms.Description: You see a cliff overlooking a forest in the Mountains. The forest is full of trees and the mountains are covered in snow. The sun is shining and the sky is blue. You can see the valley below and the river that runs through it.

Rooms.Name: Southern Horn Peak
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful mountain range with lots of snow on the ground. You see a few people walking around, but mostly You just see nature. You see the sun shining and the sky is a beautiful blue. You see soyou trees and bushes, but not many. You see soyou rocks and boulders, but not too many. Overall, You just see a lot of beauty.

Rooms.Name: A Field of Talus
Rooms.Description: You see a huge field of talus, or rock debris, that has accumulated at the base of a mountain. The talus is loose and unstable, and You have to be careful not to slip and fall. Above the talus field is a sheer cliff face, and You can see soyou climbers scaling the rock face. The view from up here is absolutely breathtaking, and You can see for miles in every direction.

Rooms.Name: A Signpost
Rooms.Description: You see a signpost in the hills. It is a wooden signpost with a metal sign on it. The sign says "A Signpost in the Hills". There is a path leading up to the signpost. The path is lined with trees. The signpost is surrounded by a field.

Rooms.Name: Nearing Orneth
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful landscape with mountains in the distance. The ground is covered in a blanket of soft, green grass. You see a few trees here and there, and a streare running through the middle of the area. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. There is a cool breeze blowing.

Rooms.Name: Within the Mist Forest
Rooms.Description: The air is thick with mist, making it hard to see more than a few feet in front of you. The forest floor is covered in a thick layer of fallen leaves, making it difficult to walk without making a lot of noise. The trees are tall and close together, making the forest feel very dark and foreboding.

Rooms.Name: Huge Granite Boulders
Rooms.Description: You see Massive boulders that have been weathered and eroded over time. Soyou of the boulders have large cracks and crevices, while others are smooth. The boulders are a variety of colors, including grey, white, and tan. The scenery is breathtaking and You can see for miles.

Rooms.Name: The Southern Worldspine
Rooms.Description: You see a long, winding path through the mountains, dotted with the occasional tree or bush. The path is mostly free of debris, though there are the occasional rocks or roots sticking up. The path is also free of people, though You occasionally see other hikers in the distance. The scenery is beautiful, with the towering mountains and the bright blue sky.

Rooms.Name: Outskirts of Marabel
Rooms.Description: You see a beautiful, serene landscape while walking along the outskirts of Marabel in the mountains. The sky is a deep blue, and the sun is shining. The trees are tall and green, and the ground is covered in a blanket of soft, green grass. You hear the sound of the wind rustling through the leaves of the trees and the sound of birds singing in the distance. You feel the warm sun on your skin and the fresh, clean air filling your lungs. You are surrounded by the beauty of nature, and You feel at peace.

Rooms.Name: A Deep Mountain Canyon
Rooms.Description: You see a deep mountain canyon with high cliffs on either side. There is a river flowing through the bottom of the canyon, and the air is cool and fresh. The scenery is breathtaking, and You feel a sense of peace and tranquility.

Rooms.Name: A Sharp Cliff Face
Rooms.Description: You see a sharp cliff face with mountains in the background. The sky is clear and blue, and the sun is shining. There is a trail leading up to the cliff face, and You can see soyou people walking up it. The trail is winding and there are soyou trees and bushes along it.
